data.title: Web Weddings: Spring 2014
data.text:
View wedding photos submitted by Dickinsonians for the spring 2014 issue of Dickinson Magazine.

Sarah Gafgen ’07 married Carl Smith of San Angelo, Texas, on Oct. 19, 2013. Sarah's bridal party included fellow Dickinson alums Karena West Mortimer ’07 as matron of honor and Shamus Hunter McCarty ’10.

Jason Tanenbaum '07 married Pamela Kimmelman on June 30, 2013. Back row, from left: Professor Jeffrey Niemitz and Trish Niemitz, Allen Castner '07, Michael Musso '06, Sean O'Mahoney '07, Jason Tanenbaum '07, Pamela Kimmelman, Matt Albanese '06, Jack and Alissa O'Shaughnessy '08 and Dave Rose '07. Front row, from left: Andrew Gardner '07, Ricky Santee '07, Tom Frame '07, Laura Bahorich '07, Adam Schantz '07, Julie Chapman '07 and Stephanie Santee '07.

Caitlin Yaeger ’11 and Henry McCorkle ’11 were married Sept. 14 in Brunswick, Maine. Dickinsonians from the classes of 1971 through 2013 joined the celebration. Standing, from left: Samem Jabarkhail '11, Russel Toris '11, John Jones '11, Andre White '11, Teddy Wilhite '12, Andrew Chesley '13, Rachel Warzala '11, Henry McCorkle '11, John Allen '11, Caitlin Yaeger '11, Kim Blank '10, Merin Yu '11, Karen Pflug-Felder '71, Caroline Fortin '11, Beth Kosta '11, Phoebe Kilgour '11, Nathan Toews '12 and Lee Tankle '10. Kneeling, from left: Luigi Fu '11, John Monopoli '11, Jeremy Keys '11, Bernadette Brandt '13, Brandon Rothenberg '11, Amanda Power '11 and Steven Seland ’11.
